sap.landvisz.LandscapeEntity.!constructorDescription:
Constructor for a new LandscapeEntity. Accepts an object literal mSettings that defines initial property values, aggregated and associated objects as well as event handlers. See {@link sap.ui.base.ManagedObject#constructor} for a general description of the syntax of the settings object.

The supported settings are:

  • Properties
    • {@link #getSystemName systemName} : string
    • {@link #getType type} : sap.landvisz.LandscapeObject
    • {@link #getQualifierText qualifierText} : string
    • {@link #getQualifierTooltip qualifierTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getQualifierType qualifierType} : string
    • {@link #getRenderingSize renderingSize} : sap.landvisz.EntityCSSSize (default: Regular)
    • {@link #getDefaultState defaultState} : string
    • {@link #getDescription description} : string
    • {@link #getActions actions} : object
    • {@link #getSystemStatus systemStatus} : sap.landvisz.ModelingStatus (default: NORMAL)
    • {@link #getStatusTooltip statusTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getExplodeViewWidth explodeViewWidth} : sap.ui.core.CSSSize
    • {@link #getExplodeViewHeight explodeViewHeight} : sap.ui.core.CSSSize
    • {@link #getShowCustomActions showCustomActions} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getShowEntityActions showEntityActions} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getSystemId systemId} : string
    • {@link #getStateIconSrc stateIconSrc} : string
    • {@link #getStateIconTooltip stateIconTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getComponentType componentType} : sap.landvisz.ComponentType
    • {@link #getComponentTypeTooltip componentTypeTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getTrackSystemCount trackSystemCount} : string
  • Aggregations
    • {@link #getDataContainers dataContainers} : sap.landvisz.internal.DataContainer[]
    • {@link #getActionBar actionBar} : sap.landvisz.internal.ActionBar[]
    • {@link #getEntityStatus entityStatus} : sap.ui.commons.Image
  • Events
    • {@link #event:mouseOverIdenIcon mouseOverIdenIcon} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:statusSelect statusSelect} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:trackInfoPress trackInfoPress} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
In addition, all settings applicable to the base type {@link sap.ui.core.Control#constructor sap.ui.core.Control} can be used as well.

Constructor for a new LandscapeViewer. Accepts an object literal mSettings that defines initial property values, aggregated and associated objects as well as event handlers. See {@link sap.ui.base.ManagedObject#constructor} for a general description of the syntax of the settings object.

The supported settings are:

    • {@link #getBoxDependencyLabel boxDependencyLabel} : string (default: Box View)
    • {@link #getBoxDependencyLevels boxDependencyLevels} : string[]
    • {@link #getShowDependencyNavigator showDependencyNavigator} : boolean (default: true)

    • {@link #getSelectionViewPosition selectionViewPosition} : sap.landvisz.SelectionViewPosition (default: CENTER)
    • {@link #getShowClose showClose} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getComponentViewLabel componentViewLabel} : string (default: Component View)
    • {@link #getDeploymentViewLabel deploymentViewLabel} : string (default: Deployment View)
    • {@link #getSolutionOptionType solutionOptionType} : sap.landvisz.OptionType
    • {@link #getSolutionType solutionType} : sap.landvisz.SolutionType
    • {@link #getShowDeploymentTypeSection showDeploymentTypeSection} : boolean (default: false)
    • {@link #getDeploymentOptionsLabel deploymentOptionsLabel} : string (default: Deployment Options :)
    • {@link #getDeploymentOptionsTooltip deploymentOptionsTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getComponentViewTooltip componentViewTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getDeploymentViewTooltip deploymentViewTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getCloseButtonTooltip closeButtonTooltip} : string

    • {@link #getConnectionLine connectionLine} : sap.landvisz.ConnectionLine (default: Line)

    • {@link #getConnectors connectors} : sap.landvisz.Connector[]
    • {@link #getSolutionOptions solutionOptions} : sap.landvisz.Option[]
